sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant CR as LLMBatchGateway CR
    participant Operator as Operator Controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Helm as HelmRenderer<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Client as External Client
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL 5432/TCP<br/>or Redis 6379/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Processor as Processor Pod
    participant InferenceGW as Inference Gateway<br/>Configurable Port

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Admin,Helm: Flow 1: LLMBatchGateway Reconciliation
        Admin->>CR: Create/Update LLMBatchGateway
        CR-->>Operator: Watch event (K8s Watch, TLS)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Lookup Secret + ReferenceGrant<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Secret data + grant status
        Operator->>Helm: Render batch-gateway chart<br/>(spec → Helm values)
        Helm-->>Operator: Rendered K8s manifests
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply<br/>(Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, etc.)<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch CR status<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Batch Inference Request Processing
        Client->>APIServer: POST /v1/batches or /v1/files<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer token
        APIServer->>DB: Store job metadata<br/>DB protocol, Optional TLS
        APIServer->>S3: Upload input files<br/>HTTPS, S3 credentials
        APIServer-->>Client: 200 OK (batch ID)

        loop Poll for pending jobs
            Processor->>DB: Query pending jobs<br/>DB protocol, Optional TLS
            DB-->>Processor: Job details
        end

        Processor->>InferenceGW: POST inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Optional inference-api-key
        InferenceGW-->>Processor: Inference result
        Processor->>S3: Write output results<br/>HTTPS, S3 credentials
        Processor->>DB: Update job status → completed
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Cross-Namespace Secret Resolution
        Operator->>K8sAPI: List ReferenceGrants<br/>in secret namespace
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: ReferenceGrant allowing<br/>batch.llm-d.ai/LLMBatchGateway
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Read source Secret
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Secret data
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed<br/>Secret copy in CR namespace<br/>(annotated batch.llm-d.ai/copied-from)
    end
